OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FBritain is expected to have sufficient
OL,8,Fgas supply to meet demand from
OL,9,Fhouseholds and businesses this summer
OL,10,Fdespite prices surging amid the
OL,11,Fconflict in the Middle East, according
OL,12,Fto the country's gas system operator.
OL,14,FNational Gas said gas stocks in Great
OL,15,FBritain are set to be sufficient
OL,16,Fenough to allow for some British gas
OL,17,Fto exported to mainland Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
