OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FThe body, which runs Britain's
OL,8,FNational Transmission System (NTS),
OL,9,Funveiled its outlook for summer 2026
OL,10,Famid a volatile backdrop for global
OL,11,Fenergy markets.
OL,13,FThe price of oil and gas has jumped
OL,14,Fsharply since the start of the
OL,15,Fconflict between US-Israeli and
OL,16,FIranian forces in late February.
OL,18,FUK natural gas futures had risen to
OL,19,Faround 120.7 pence per therm on
OL,20,FMonday, up from around 78 pence per
OL,21,Ftherm before the conflict began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FA number of liquified natural gas
OL,8,F(LNG) production facilities in Qatar
OL,9,Fand other parts of the Middle East
OL,10,Fhave been targeted by missiles, while
OL,11,Fexports from the region have also been
OL,12,Fimpacted by heavy disruption to the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz shipping corridor.
OL,15,FNational Gas stressed that British
OL,16,Fdemand for gas will be primarily met
OL,17,Fby supplies extracted from the UK
OL,18,FContinental Shelf and imports from
OL,19,FNorway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FAround 86% of total gas supply (25.3
OL,8,Fbcm) is expected to come from these
OL,9,Fsources.
OL,11,FNational Gas said it expects this
OL,12,Fvolume will be enough to exceed
OL,13,Fforecast demand from Great Britain and
OL,14,Fgas exported to Ireland.
OL,16,FNevertheless, it added that around 5%
OL,17,Fof total supply will also come from
OL,18,Fflexible gas storage and around 9% of
OL,19,Fsupply will come from LNG imports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FForecasts were prepared ahead of the
OL,8,Fescalation of the conflict in the
OL,9,FMiddle East but National Gas said it
OL,10,Fhas reviewed its analysis since and
OL,11,Fconcluded that the market is expected
OL,12,Fto still have sufficient capacity and
OL,13,Fcapability to meet forecasts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FGlenn Bryn-Jacobsen, director of
OL,8,Fenergy systems and resilience at
OL,9,FNational Gas, said: "While the
OL,10,Fsituation in the Middle East has
OL,11,Funderstandably raised questions about
OL,12,FBritain's gas supplies, our forecasts
OL,13,Findicate the market has the capacity
OL,14,Fto deliver sufficient supply to meet
OL,15,Fdemand this summer.
OL,17,F"The diversity of supply sources,
OL,18,Fincluding domestic production, Norway,
OL,19,FLNG and storage, provides resilience
OL,20,Fand flexibility as supply flows and
OL,21,Fdemand patterns change."
OL,26,@qD@UOUyD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FDemand for gas is forecast to be
OL,8,Fsimilar to summer 2025, according to
OL,9,Fthe projections.
OL,11,FNational Gas expects a roughly 6%
OL,12,Freduction in gas demand used for
OL,13,Felectricity generation but said this
OL,14,Fwill be largely offset by an expected
OL,15,F2% rise in non-daily metered demand
OL,16,Ffrom residential and commercial
OL,17,Fconsumers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FIan Radley, chief commercial officer
OL,8,Fat National Gas, said: "Gas continues
OL,9,Fto play a critical role in supporting
OL,10,Fthe electricity system, even during
OL,11,Fthe summer months.
OL,13,F"As renewable output fluctuates,
OL,14,Fgasfired power stations are
OL,15,Fincreasingly required to respond
OL,16,Fquickly, and the network must be able
OL,17,Fto support that safely and reliably.
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
