OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776183067
OL,3,CGas supplies 'can meet British demand
OL,4,Cover summer' despite Iran war
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,F"It is important that ongoing, co-
OL,8,Fordinated action between Government,
OL,9,Findustry and regulators continues to
OL,10,Faddress future risks arising from
OL,11,Fdeclining domestic production and an
OL,12,Fincreasing reliance on imports."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]
